          "text": "Summer into AI 2026"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " hosted by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "@advisoryhour"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " — theme: Built on Yesterday."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Convention let five Founding Fathers debate a single topic in a single round. The Founders' Court upgrades the whole experience: six modern constitutional controversies, extended thinking rendered live in each founder's column so you can watch Hamilton and Jefferson actually reason before they argue, and ElevenLabs voices so Madison sounds like Madison."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Worth noting alongside this: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "Other week-4 entries"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " upgraded visual polish; Founders' Court upgraded the AI depth — making the reasoning itself part of the show"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How the AI works"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Parallel extended thinking streams"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — all five founders stream simultaneously via SSE. Each column shows a collapsible 'Reasoning' panel that expands when thinking tokens arrive, so you see Washington deliberating in real time before he speaks."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Vote detection mid-stream"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — Claude is instructed to embed [VOTE:FOR] or [VOTE:AGAINST] in its text. The frontend parses these as they stream and immediately updates the tally board."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "ElevenLabs voice synthesis"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — each founder has a unique ElevenLabs voice ID. After their argument completes, click SPEAK to hear their verdict in their voice."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How to play"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Pick one of six modern constitutional controversies — from AI regulation to term limits."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Watch all five founders stream their arguments simultaneously. Click any 'Reasoning' panel to expand the extended thinking."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The tally board at the top updates live as each "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "[VOTE]"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is detected in the stream."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Click SPEAK on any founder to hear their verdict read aloud. The final verdict reveals how the republic would have ruled."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
